Sentencas: A dense and crack-free La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta thin film has been prepared by RF magnetron sputtering.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: The XRD, FESEM, XPS and four-probe technique are employed to characterize the La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta film.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: Results show that after annealing at 1000 degrees C, the La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta film presents a polycrystalline perovskite structure with grain size of 100-300 nm.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: XPS data show that both La and Ga are in their +3 state.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: Sr element has two chemical states which are related to Sr2- in the perovskite lattice and SrO1-delta suboxide.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: The O 1s spectrum also shows two chemical states which can be assigned to molecularly adsorbed O-2 species and O2- in the lattice.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity reaches to 0.093 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC

Sentencas: The microstructure and conductivity analysis indicates that the La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta thin film prepared by RF magnetron sputtering is suitable for intermediate temperature Solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-δ thin film on the porous cathode for SOFC
